### =========================================================================
### 🛠️ 1. Direct Manual Ticket Issuance (Admin Only)
### =========================================================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets/issue
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "bookingId": {{sampleBookingId}},
  "eventId": {{sampleEventId}},
  "nationalId": {{sampleNationalId}},
  "quantity": 2
}

### =========================================================================
### 📱 2. In-App Mobile Wallet Sync (Any Authenticated User)
### =========================================================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets/my-passes/{{sampleNationalId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### =========================================================================
### 🎟️ 3. Gate Validation Scanner - Clean Initial Entry (Admin Only)
### =========================================================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets/verify
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "ticketToken": "{{sampleGeneratedToken}}"
}

### =========================================================================
### ⚠️ 4. Gate Validation Scanner - Double-Entry Guard Test (Admin Only)
### =========================================================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets/verify
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "ticketToken": "{{sampleGeneratedToken}}"
}

### =========================================================================
### ❌ 5. Malformed Request Validation Test
### =========================================================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets/verify
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "ticketToken": ""
}

### =========================================================================
### 📊 6. Event Statistics / Gate Progress Monitor (Admin Only)
### =========================================================================
# Verifies the count of scanned/unscanned tickets and the percentage completion.
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets/stats/{{sampleEventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}